nodes.text: ZD-10-9 was a TIE pilot of the Galactic Empire.

Sometime following 0 BBY, ZD-10-9 was part of a TIE pilot unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
ZD-10-9 was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2009, 10, and 11.
